<section>
  <title>What else should we know about the quizzes and exams?</title>

  <ul>
    <li>Check OAKS frequently for due dates. No separate announcements will be sent for quizzes or tests.</li>

    <li>Quizzes will be online and posted in OAKS.</li>

    <li>
      There is <term>no make-up possible for tests or quizzes</term> under any circumstances. 
      One missed test grade may be replaced by the Final Exam grade only if the absence is due to 
      severe circumstances such as serious illness, family emergencies, or quarantine. 
      If such events are anticipated, notify the instructor as soon as possible.
    </li>

    <li>
      Solutions for quizzes or exams may not be provided. 
      Students are encouraged to use office hours to receive feedback on their performance.
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>